rComments: I loved this class and I'm so glad that I took it. It was a great experience for me since this is the first time in my program that I've had a math professor that made me so interested and passionate about the course material. Professor Broadbent is a great lecturer and she also cares a lot about students. She is the best professor I've ever had.
I loved this professor. She really cared for her students and was very accessible after class. The weight of the midterms and the exams should've been different but other than that I recommend her.

Professor Anne has been a great teacher. Presented course material in a very clear way and even the flow of topics was great. Very responsive to emails as well. Overall great prof. Maybe weightage of individual tests and final exams might bring down your marks a little. But this class is an easy A with Prof Anne
Probably one of the worst professors I've had in University. The course is easy so you can just skip the lectures and read the free provided textbook yourself.
